653479943", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8d3/0e5a/107187_normal.png?m=1653479943", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8d3/0e5a/107187_large.png?m=1653479943", "created": 1427200639, "last_modified": 1653479943}, "last_reply_by": "sun1993", "last_touched": 1658806474, "title": "长期熬夜想调整作息，褪黑素有用吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868528", "created": 1658727483, "deleted": 0, "content": "长期凌晨三点以后睡，下午一两点起。想要调整作息。尝试过强行早睡，但是发现实在是睡不着，太痛苦了。于是想要试试褪黑素，但是又怕产生依赖。", "content_rendered": "长期凌晨三点以后睡，下午一两点起。想要调整作息。尝试过强行早睡，但是发现实在是睡不着，太痛苦了。于是想要试试褪黑素，但是又怕产生依赖。", "last_modified": 1658736972, "replies": 88, "id": 868528}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_large.png?m=1648339948", "name": "python", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_normal.png?m=1648339948", "title": "Python", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/python", "topics": 15045, "footer": "", "header": "这里讨论各种 Python 语言编程话题，也包括 Django，Tornado 等框架的讨论。这里是一个能够帮助你解决实际问题的地方。", "title_alternative": "Python", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_mini.png?m=1648339948", "stars": 10010, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 90, "parent_node_name": "programming"}, "member": {"id": 254827, "username": "wcsjtu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wcsjtu", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7bfe93d15f215a020758a2fd0ceeaea6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7bfe93d15f215a020758a2fd0ceeaea6?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7bfe93d15f215a020758a2fd0ceeaea6?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1505636707, "last_modified": 1505636707}, "last_reply_by": "changz", "last_touched": 1658809538, "title": "请问大家, 有没有办法把 Python 的 dict, 存储到一段连续内存上", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868557", "created": 1658732912, "deleted": 0, "content": "比如说, 我这里有个 \r\n\r\n```python\r\ntable: Dict[str, List[str]] = {\r\n\t\"key1\": [\"value1\", \"value2\", ...],\r\n    ...,\r\n    \"keyn\": [\"valuem\", ...]\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n我想把这个 dict 中的所有对象(包括所有的 key, value, 以及 list), 全部存储到一段连续内存里, 同时还能支持查表操作, 比如说\r\n\r\n```python\r\nvalues: List[str] = table_in_contigious_memory[\"key1\"]\r\n```\r\n\r\n有没有现成的轮子可以做这种事啊。\r\n\r\nPS: 可以不是 Python 原生的 Dict, 只要是 dict-like, 支持查表就行.....", "content_rendered": "<p>比如说, 我这里有个 </p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">table: Dict[str, List[str]] = {\n\t\"key1\": [\"value1\", \"value2\", ...],\n    ...,\n    \"keyn\": [\"valuem\", ...]\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>我想把这个 dict 中的所有对象(包括所有的 key, value, 以及 list), 全部存储到一段连续内存里, 同时还能支持查表操作, 比如说</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\">values: List[str] = table_in_contigious_memory[\"key1\"]\n</code></pre>\n<p>有没有现成的轮子可以做这种事啊。</p>\n<p>PS: 可以不是 Python 原生的 Dict, 只要是 dict-like, 支持查表就行.....</p>\n", "last_modified": 1658732912, "replies": 82, "id": 868557}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_large.png?m=1650095354", "name": "security", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_normal.png?m=1650095354", "title": "信息安全", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/security", "topics": 1361, "footer": "", "header": "我们都希望自己管理的计算机系统在运转过程中不要遇到任何安全事件。只是，这个不完美的世界的现实告诉我们：学无止境。", "title_alternative": "Security", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1650095354", "stars": 1537, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 260, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 326853, "username": "nemo95", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nemo95", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8a4/6b77/326853_mini.png?m=1532055494", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8a4/6b77/326853_normal.png?m=1532055494", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e8a4/6b77/326853_large.png?m=1532055494", "created": 1530702537, "last_modified": 1532055494}, "last_reply_by": "chrisia", "last_touched": 1658810323, "title": "因为路由器刷了 padavan，智障公司通报我挖矿", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868561", "created": 1658733571, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天虎王行动第一天，网安通报了一批涉嫌挖矿的 ip ，都是通过探针发现有访问 https://bitbucket.org/的行为\r\n\r\n然后我解释这应该是我路由器在检查更新，但他们还是让我把路由关了等过两周再用，说这名单是集团公司给的他们也不懂不好解释……\r\n\r\n是不是现在带 bit 的域名都不能打开了", "content_rendered": "<p>今天虎王行动第一天，网安通报了一批涉嫌挖矿的 ip ，都是通过探针发现有访问 <a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bitbucket.org/的行为</a></p>\n<p>然后我解释这应该是我路由器在检查更新，但他们还是让我把路由关了等过两周再用，说这名单是集团公司给的他们也不懂不好解释……</p>\n<p>是不是现在带 bit 的域名都不能打开了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1658733571, "replies": 58, "id": 868561}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1656605007", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1656605007", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49968, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007", "stars": 7911, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 506259, "username": "silypie", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/silypie", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e2f1dbb036de1978c1ddaffbd8435018?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1598965543, "last_modified": 1658109458}, "last_reply_by": "HappyFox", "last_touched": 1658807109, "title": "垂直鼠标真的比普通的鼠标好用吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868534", "created": 1658728591, "deleted": 0, "content": "用