求如何被满足呢？</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>而且虽然微信存在一些问题，真的有必要摒弃它吗？</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>以上是我的真诚的一些发问，没有质疑的意思，有些不明就里，真心希望得到问题的解答。</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果可以，也希望大家就自己的微信及其他社交工具的使用情况 简单聊聊，做个参考。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1658798502, "replies": 53, "id": 868696}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1656605007", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1656605007", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49968, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1656605007", "stars": 7911, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 220603, "username": "liuidetmks", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liuidetmks", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_mini.png?m=1658734207", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_normal.png?m=1658734207", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_large.png?m=1658734207", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_xlarge.png?m=1658734207", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_xlarge.png?m=1658734207", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e540/71e7/220603_xlarge.png?m=1658734207", "created": 1489372952, "last_modified": 1658734207}, "last_reply_by": "go522000", "last_touched": 1658805550, "title": "买了个域名，请问有什么好的创业项目吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868612", "created": 1658741864, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1658741864, "replies": 43, "id": 868612}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340